# Workflow Builder Product Document

## Overview

Commenda provides various services such as US C Corp and India Pvt Ltd Incorporations, along with filings like Delaware Franchise Tax, IRS 1120, and Sales tax. Currently, most services are handled via service requests. However, as our service offerings expand, managing and updating these requests becomes time-consuming. Even simple task additions require extensive deployment, testing, and release efforts, proving unscalable. The Workflow Builder addresses this by enabling rapid service creation and deployment through an intuitive drag-and-drop editor.

## Components of the workflow builder

There are several components involved in the workflow builder.

### Workflow Management

In this module, you can manage your existing workflows, including creating new workflows, developing different versions, publishing, activating, and linking them to different areas of our product. You can find it on the workflow management tab in the admin.

![][image1]

### Workflow Editor

This module allows you to build a specific workflow version. It provides a canvas where you can drag and drop and connect various steps (nodes) to design your workflow. Each step offers customizable configurations.

![][image2]

### Workflow Visualizer

This module allows the users of the workflow to take actionable items on each step.

![][image3]
